description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Breath Focused Restore' from the channel Owen Henn.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The The Zen Flow vibe means Grounding, intentional, breath-centered, unhurried. This is especially good for When you need balance, mindfulness, and release. The The Deep Recharge vibe means Nervous system reset, ultra-gentle movement. This is especially good for Times of extreme stress, fatigue, or mental overload..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let your breath guide your practice with Owen in this restorative session. ...
